_sText: Hi, this is my first map. This was just a test at first, but I thought it was pretty good, so I improved it and released. I hope you enjoy it! Just break the huge crates with the awp, grenades, glock or knife (takes 4 hits from awp, a lot more from grenades, glock or knife) and lots of guns and flashbangs fall. Then navigate through the obstacles to find the other team and kill them!
